#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/cdi.adoc:319
msgid "A bean class may declare lifecycle `@PostConstruct` and `@PreDestroy` callbacks:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Block title
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/cdi.adoc:320
#, no-wrap
